            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Lost Bids</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">You submit bids but never follow up effectively. Clients go with whoever stays in touch.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
