            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Communication Gaps</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Clients feel ignored mid-project. They call constantly asking for updates you forgot to send.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">No Documentation</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Progress photos exist in your phone. Clients don't see them. Your work isn't showcased.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
