          <p class="text-slate-600">Satisfied clients don't think to refer. No system, no incentives, no systematic growth.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Long Sales Cycles</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Big projects take months to close. Without nurturing, leads go cold.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solution Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
